modules.description: Handles C-stub compilation and OPAM package configuration for GTK bindings, managing separate packages for each C library. Processes Dune files to automate build setup and ensure reproducibility. Facilitates release workflows by structuring dependencies and build targets explicitly.

Attaches and manages spell checking to a GtkTextView, allowing language configuration and manual rechecking of text. It operates on GtkTextView widgets and handles errors through exceptions. Use it to enable real-time spelling validation in text editing interfaces.
